{"tid":1695151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足有事手好嬲？但今日大家要做既唔係開花","createTime":"2019-11-05T13:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:06:08.000Z","uid":81236,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bffc96f86608d117e58f1405eabbb5d260c8fe5","tid":1695151,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"唔係要開花將大家既憤怒發洩<br />\n<br />\n而係將大家既憤怒累積<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為對抗極權政府做更多既準備工作</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">同時為手足祈禱，為佢集氣。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以話我係休息撚，但希望大家知道同學呢一刻需要既唔係大家開花，唔係淨係堵路，唔係淨係叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n今日開花只會有兩個結果<br />\n<br />\n1）警甴放軟手腳，比市民發洩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">然後聽日就好嬲咁繼續返工返學</span></span><br />\n聽日全部焦點都去晒開花<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）更暴力既手段，製造另一個周同學<br />\n用其他暴力事件掩蓋呢件事，令到香港市民分身不暇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果周同學有咩事，作為一條導火線，市民要準備充足<br />\n<br />\n1）大罷工準備<br />\n幫手成立工會，特別係要推廣公務員工會<br />\n<br />\n2）黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n3）罷課籌備組<br />\n<br />\n等等..."},{"pid":"0d955b7e252e37cb1dda644b93caec0aff0da63a","tid":1695151,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWpaL58.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWpaL58.png&h=64e590ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約定你11月6 Sogo崇光百貨感謝祭 下午三點銅鑼灣見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5619d71a1f5e7af2257de96d815ae2ca77cee2ba","tid":1695151,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:04:41.000Z","msg":"祈禱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你條仆街做宣明會嫁?"},{"pid":"a13f710f0c3ae3026228c779b20d3d363ebeebeb","tid":1695151,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}